casebody.data:
The State ex rel. Jackson, Appellant, v. Dallman, Warden, Appellee.

[Cite as State ex rel. Jackson v. Dallman (1994), 71 Ohio St.3d. 400.]

(No. 94-1719 Submitted November 29, 1994 Decided December 30, 1994.) Nathaniel Jackson, pro se. Lee Fisher, Attorney General, and John J. Gideon, Assistant Attorney General, for appellee. Per Curiam.

The decision of the court of appeals is affirmed on authority of Wenzel v. Enright (1993), 68 Ohio St.3d 63, 623 N.E.2d 69.

Judgment affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
